| Attendance (Self) | âœ… | âœ… | âŒ | âŒ |
| Attendance (Own Dept) | âŒ | âœ… | âŒ | âŒ |
| Leave Requests (Own Dept) | âŒ | âœ… | âœ… | âŒ |
Specific Permissions:
- âœ… View dashboard with department-specific data
- âœ… View employees in managed department
- âœ… Check-in/Check-out (self-service)
- âœ… View attendance for department employees
- âœ… Approve/Deny leave requests for department employees only
- âœ… View own profile and attendance history
- âœ… View company holidays
- âœ… Generate department-specific reports
Restrictions:
- âŒ Cannot add/edit/delete employees
- âŒ Cannot manage departments or shifts
- âŒ Cannot create/edit holidays
- âŒ Cannot approve leave requests outside their department
- âŒ Cannot access system-wide configuration
- âŒ Cannot delete any data
- âŒ Cannot mark attendance for others
Use Cases:
- Department Manager reviewing team attendance
- Supervisor approving subordinate leave requests
- Team Lead monitoring department performance
8.3 EMPLOYEE Role
Login Credentials:
UserID: 3
Username: ndhai
Password: 123456
Role: EMPLOYEE
Self-Service Access:
Feature	Create	Read	Update	Delete
Own Profile	âŒ	âœ…	âŒ	âŒ
