â€¢	âœ… Check-In with shift selection
â€¢	âœ… Check-Out
â€¢	âœ… View personal attendance history
â€¢	âœ… Submit leave requests (Annual, Medical, Personal)
â€¢	âœ… View leave request status (Pending/Approved/Rejected)
â€¢	âœ… Edit pending leave requests
â€¢	âœ… View own profile information
â€¢	âœ… View company holiday calendar
â€¢	âœ… View own shift schedule
Restrictions:
â€¢	âŒ Cannot view other employees' data
â€¢	âŒ Cannot edit attendance records
â€¢	âŒ Cannot mark attendance for others
â€¢	âŒ Cannot approve/deny any leave requests
â€¢	âŒ Cannot access employee list
â€¢	âŒ Cannot access department management
â€¢	âŒ Cannot access shift management
â€¢	âŒ Cannot access admin features
â€¢	âŒ Cannot view dashboard (redirected to own profile)
Use Cases:
â€¢	Employee recording daily attendance
â€¢	Staff member requesting vacation time
â€¢	Worker viewing personal attendance history
Page Access Matrix
Page	ADMIN	MANAGER	EMPLOYEE
