â€¢	GET /api/employees - List all (ADMIN/MANAGER)
â€¢	GET /api/employees/{id} - Get single employee
â€¢	POST /api/employees - Create new (ADMIN only)
â€¢	PUT /api/employees/{id} - Update (ADMIN only)
â€¢	DELETE /api/employees/{id} - Delete (ADMIN only)
