â€¢	Department name required
â€¢	Location required
â€¢	Manager ID must exist in employee table
Business Rules:
1.	Department name must be unique
2.	One manager per department
3.	Cannot delete department with active employees
4.	Manager must be an employee in the system
API Endpoints:
â€¢	GET /api/departments - List all departments
â€¢	GET /api/departments/{id} - Get department details
â€¢	POST /api/departments - Create department (ADMIN)
â€¢	PUT /api/departments/{id} - Update department (ADMIN)
â€¢	DELETE /api/departments/{id} - Delete department (ADMIN)
â€¢	GET /api/departments/{id}/employees - List employees in department
