Shift List Table:
Shift ID	Shift Name	Start Time	End Time	Actions
1	Morning Shift	06:00 AM	02:00 PM	Delete
2	Day Shift	08:00 AM	05:00 PM	Delete
3	Evening Shift	02:00 PM	10:00 PM	Delete
4	Night Shift	10:00 PM	06:00 AM	Delete
Pre-defined Shift Types:
1.	Morning Shift: 06:00 - 14:00
2.	Day Shift: 08:00 - 17:00
3.	Evening Shift: 14:00 - 22:00
4.	Night Shift: 22:00 - 06:00
Features:
â€¢	âœ… Create custom shifts
â€¢	âœ… Define start/end times
â€¢	âœ… Delete shifts (if not in use)
â€¢	âœ… Assign employees to shifts (from Employees page)
Form Validation:
â€¢	Shift name required
â€¢	Start time required
â€¢	End time required
â€¢	End time must be different from start time
Business Rules:
1.	Cannot delete shift assigned to employees
2.	Shift name should be descriptive
3.	Support for overnight shifts (night shift)
API Endpoints:
â€¢	GET /api/shifts - List all shifts
â€¢	GET /api/shifts/{id} - Get shift details
â€¢	POST /api/shifts - Create shift (ADMIN)
â€¢	PUT /api/shifts/{id} - Update shift (ADMIN)
â€¢	DELETE /api/shifts/{id} - Delete shift (ADMIN)
