â€¢	âœ… Add company holidays
â€¢	âœ… Automatic attendance marking as "Holiday" for all employees
â€¢	âœ… View holiday calendar
â€¢	âœ… Delete holidays
Form Validation:
â€¢	Holiday name required
â€¢	Date required
â€¢	Date cannot be in the past
Business Rules:
1.	All employees automatically marked as "Holiday" status
2.	No attendance marking required on holidays
3.	Holidays apply company-wide
Sync Feature:
â€¢	When holiday is added, system auto-creates attendance records with "Holiday" status for all active employees
API Endpoints:
â€¢	GET /api/holidays - List all holidays
â€¢	GET /api/holidays/{id} - Get holiday details
â€¢	POST /api/holidays - Create holiday (ADMIN)
â€¢	PUT /api/holidays/{id} - Update holiday (ADMIN)
â€¢	DELETE /api/holidays/{id} - Delete holiday (ADMIN)
â€¢	POST /api/holidays/sync-attendance?holidayId={id} - Sync attendance
